metadata.name: Finch Pendant
metadata.description:
Finches have accompanied mankind for centuries. As bright warbling ambassadors of the beauty of nature, they have never failed to uplift those who encounter them. People who feel especially connected to finches may be drawn to the vibrant colors or cheerful songs for which these birds are known.
Symbolically, finches have many interesting meanings depending on culture and context. Many traditional wisdoms and sayings associate finches with rainfall and premonition.

Due to their popularity as pets, finches are often associated with captivity as well as freedom.
